attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: This stunning brick-and-beam residence is a dream home for those who appreciate space, style, and the convenience of city living. Located in a dramatic corner unit, the loft offers oversized windows with sweeping city views, abundant natural light and an exceptional layout ideal for both entertaining and working from home. Featuring 11-foot ceilings, exposed brick, warm maple wood floors, a designated dining area and a large kitchen with stainless steel appliances and ample storage. The spacious living room flows seamlessly into a sunny office with a cleverly integrated Murphy bed, perfect for accommodating guests. The primary bedroom includes a custom walk-in California Closet, while the renovated bathroom boasts modern shower tiles and fixtures. Central heat/ac, in-unit washer/dryer and heated tandem garage parking round out this offering! Located in Fort Point Place, a highly desirable elevator building in the heart of vibrant Fort Point, just a few blocks from the Seaport District!
